lead_paragraph: Newcastle United's advantage at the top of the Championship, England's second division, was cut to two points as they fell to a shock 1-0 home defeat to Blackburn Rovers on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Newcastle Streak Ends as Blackburn Stun Leaders
